originalText.text:
Dr. Lourdes Dominguez is a
"Five Star" psychiatrist. Right from the start, her office was professional and accommodating. From the moment she greeted me, I felt comfortable and trusting.  I had instant connectivity and great hope that she understood my problem and left me confident that she could help. She's intuitive, has great listening skills and extensive knowledge of the most up-to-date therapies/medications available. She took time to educate and explain the differences and side effects of each therapy/medication she recommended. Her extensive experience,  education, knowledge, compassion, humility and unique personality makes her a leader in her field of Psychiatry. Simply the best!
